snippet: A decades-old urban legend was put to rest Saturday when workers for a documentary film production company recovered "E.T." Atari game cartridges from a heap of garbage buried deep in the New Mexico desert....

headline.print_headline: Diggers Find Atari's E.T. Games in Landfill
headline.main: Diggers Find Atari's E.T. Games in Landfill

lead_paragraph: A decades-old urban legend was put to rest Saturday when workers for a documentary film production company recovered "E.T." Atari game cartridges from a heap of garbage buried deep in the New Mexico desert.
